# TODO

Current phase tasks.

## Phase 4: Publisher CLI

### 4a: CLI Foundation ✅
- [x] Create CLI entry point (src/cli/index.js)
- [x] Parse command line arguments (--help, --version)
- [x] Support subcommands: publish, derive, validate, list

### 4b: Publish Command ✅
- [x] `tref publish <content>` - create and publish block
- [x] `tref publish -f <file>` - publish from file
- [x] `tref publish --stdin` - read content from stdin
- [x] Options: --refs (add references), --license, --pretty

### 4c: Derive Command ✅
- [x] `tref derive <parent-id> <content>` - derive from parent
- [x] `tref derive -f <parent.tref> <content>` - derive from file
- [x] Preserve parent refs automatically

### 4d: Validate Command ✅
- [x] `tref validate <file.tref>` - validate block integrity
- [x] Check ID matches content hash
- [x] Check schema compliance
- [x] Exit codes: 0=valid, 1=invalid

### 4e: List/Info Commands ✅
- [x] `tref list` - list all published blocks
- [x] `tref info <id>` - show block details
- [x] `tref cat <id>` - output block content

### 4f: MCP Server ✅
- [x] MCP server wrapper for AI integration
- [x] Tools: tref_publish, tref_derive, tref_validate, tref_list, tref_info, tref_cat
